{"tid":649809,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得應該畀未補地價居屋合法出租？？？","createTime":"2018-05-01T22:23:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T11:11:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"8ecca5ad7a69f8ed035ead565d25b1c5ad85bb20","tid":649809,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T22:23:10.000Z","msg":"最多分番一半租金畀政府姐，點解要禁止出租咁野蠻？？明明層樓真金白銀買"},{"pid":"76dc05b20d8608b163dfec18cb3dd47eb4a41b24","tid":649809,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T22:33:14.000Z","msg":"不許在市場上出租的。但事實上，市場上有不少未補地價居屋出租。有些租予業主的親友，有些市場上出租。明知違法，卻仍然出租。因為有實際需要，社會又有需求。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n在居屋業主而言，可能不再居住單位。可以回大陸居住，又或與子女同住。居屋丟空很可惜，要補地價出租又不化算。於是被迫違法出租，是一種社會矛盾。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n如果容許未補地價居屋合法出租，可以化解部份社會矛盾。但可能衍生新矛盾，就是衝擊私樓業主的出租利益。所以出租未補地價居屋，必須透過社企進行。"},{"pid":"c8d13ee9ddbea49831ef9de52d16a12ef9130065","tid":649809,"uid":155732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T22:42:08.000Z","msg":"政府有心推高樓價<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c14d13c8924478163c4d4c3c40ef5e8aeacc12f","tid":649809,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T22:43:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府：你唔鍾意可以唔買居屋</span></span>"},{"pid":"c51333a51abd313c9e70ef7df2248c3af0f6e371","tid":649809,"uid":68556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T23:26:09.000Z","msg":"買之前已經講明未補地價不可出租。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"069bb3d095991f9aacf16f46f001f25cde595920","tid":649809,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c51333a51abd313c9e70ef7df2248c3af0f6e371","tid":649809,"uid":68556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T23:26:09.000Z","msg":"買之前已經講明未補地價不可出租。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class